snippet.title: Die, Master Monkey
snippet.description:
An avant-garde performance artist working exclusively with low-tech, lo-fi, analog and trash. Always Live, Always Lo, Always Free.

** What People Say **
"Not normal."
"Like watching a painting."
"Christian Wolff on amphetamines."
"Laurie Anderson meets Black Flag."

** Master Monkey Must Die Everywhere **

Twitter - https://twitter.com/diemastermonkey
Twitch - https://twitch.tv/diemastermonkey
Google+ - https://plus.google.com/u/1/109770018877772601370/posts

** Live Performance Rig **
Roland SP-404 SX Linear Wave Sampler
Roland SP-202 "Dr. Sample" Phrase Sampler
Arturia MicroBrute Analog Synthesizer
Casio SK-1 (unmodified)
Various monkey-bent instruments
Yamaha electric guitar
Ibanez electric bass guitar
Old films, found sounds, detuned radios, clock mechanisms, and kitchenware.
